Package doa.engine.input

Class DoaKeyboard

java.lang.Object
doa.engine.input.DoaKeyboard
public final class DoaKeyboard extends Object
Responsible for catching all fired keyboard inputs at any logical frame. This class is static, therefore has no objects.
Since:
DoaEngine 1.0
Version:
3.0
Author:
Doga Oruc
